  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd. \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Jaffna. Land acquisition for sailors halted in Karainagar!",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Attempts to acquire public land for a naval base in Karainagar, Jaffna, have been abandoned by popular opposition.",
        "An attempt was made to set up a naval base on a privately owned land in the Neelankadu area in the Karainagar J / 145 Grama Niladhari Division on Tuesday the 28th.",
        "The land survey work has been suspended due to protests by the people's representatives and the public."
      ],
